# POC-ROOT

------------------------------
Spring BOOT
------------------------------
Using application.properties in POC-BOOT to customize URL.
To run project:
java -jar POC-BOOT\target\POC-BOOT-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar
Then reach url:
http://localhost:8080/POC/rest/srv/obj

------------------------------
Spring + Tomcat
------------------------------
cd POC-WEB
mvn package tomcat7:deploy
mvn package tomcat7:redeploy

